    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>medium egg noodles</strong> to a pot and cover with<strong> boiled water </strong>until fully submerged</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 5-6 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain and set aside</p>",
