    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat and add the <strong>chopped pepper </strong>and<strong> mangetout</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until the pepper is beginning to soften</p><p>Trim, then slice the <strong>spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
